            <Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
              <Heading>Abstract</Heading>
              <Para>We study the linear relaxation Boltzmann equation, a simple semiclassical kinetic model. We provide a resolvent estimate for an associated non-selfadjoint operator as well as an estimate on the return to equilibrium. This is done using a scaling argument and non-semiclassical hypocoercive estimate.</Para>
            </Abstract>
